<p>7. Joel Gehrke, “State Department preparing for clash of civilizations with China,” Washington Examiner, April 30, 2019 ;斯金纳于2019年8月初因“虐待下属”被解职。Joel Gehrke, “Mike Pompeo fires top State Department official accused of abusing staff,” Washington Examiner, August 2, 2019. </p>
